<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<h2 id="getting-ready-for-brexit">Getting ready for Brexit</h2>

<p>Watch an hour long webinar about 5 key areas UK businesses must be aware of to keep trading goods when the UK leaves the EU.</p>

<p>The video covers:</p>

<ul>
  <li>applying for an <abbr title="Economic Operator Registration and Identification">EORI</abbr> number</li>
  <li>preparing to make customs declarations</li>
  <li>transitional simplified procedures</li>
  <li>entry summary declarations (also known as safety and security declarations)</li>
  <li>paying customs duty, VAT and Excise</li>
</ul>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0k9rcQvgetw">Geting ready for Brexit</a></p>

<h2 id="importing-goods">Importing goods</h2>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yxByCHjy934">Importing goods from the EU to the UK in a no-deal Brexit in 10 steps</a></p>

<h2 id="exporting-goods">Exporting goods</h2>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lgi0XKJRp3I&feature=youtu.be">Exporting goods from the UK to the EU in a no-deal Brexit in 10 steps</a></p>

<p>Use <a rel="external" href="https://online.hmrc.gov.uk/webchatprod/assistant/bot/Ruth">HMRC’s automated assistant Ask Ruth</a> for answers to simple questions.</p>

</div>
</div>


